[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0229","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0098","title":"Sendmail SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sendmail SMTP 服务在处理 HELO 命令时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制的 HELO 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可导致任意代码执行或服务崩溃，攻击者借此可完全控制服务器或隐藏恶意活动痕迹。该漏洞影响多个版本的 Sendmail，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0098"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.903","remediation":"立即升级 Sendmail 至 8.9.0 或更高版本（该版本修复了 SMTP HELO 命令缓冲区溢出问题）。SLMail 用户应升级至 3.0 及以上版本，Mercury Mail Server 用户升级至最新版本。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙层面限制 SMTP（TCP 25）端口仅允许可信来源访问，同时在 Sendmail 配置中限制 HELO 命令输入长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0098"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0229.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0003","title":"Common Desktop Environment ToolTalk RPC 服务缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk 数据库服务器（rpc.ttdbserverd）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标系统发送特制请求即可触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Xi Graphics Maximum CDE 1.2.3、TriTeal TED CDE 4.3 及 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 等系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，属于当年最具破坏力的远程代码执行漏洞之一。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0003"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-04-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:18.353","remediation":"立即禁用 rpc.ttdbserverd 服务（进程名：rpc.ttdbserverd），执行 /usr/bin/killall rpc.ttdbserverd 终止进程，并从 /etc/inetd.conf（或 /etc/xinetd.d/）中注释 rstatd/rusersd 相关行后重启 inetd。对于 SGI IRIX，应安装 SGI 安全公告 19981101-01 中提供的补丁。对于 Sun Solaris 系统，应用 Sun 提供的对应安全补丁（如 SunOS 5.5.1 相关补丁）。上述操作系统均已终止安全支持，强烈建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/122","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19102","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0003","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/572.txt","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0003.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0003.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w/GHSA-gxwg-52wj-vc7w.json","https://github.com/FIRSTdotorg/Vuln4Cast/blob/c93910d268aa5b5d2260adb9b5d92094b2d06daf/YearlyVuln4Cast-V1.ipynb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0152","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0060","title":"Lucent Ascend 系列路由器 Discard Service 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Lucent Ascend MAX 5.0/Pipeline 6.0/TNT 1.0/2.0 路由器存在拒绝服务漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标路由器的 discard 端口（UDP 端口 9，被 Java Configurator 工具使用）发送特制的畸形数据包，即可触发该漏洞，导致路由器服务崩溃或无法正常响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Lucent Ascend MAX、Pipeline 及 TNT 系列路由器，需引起相关运维人员重视。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0060"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.030","remediation":"在受影响路由器上配置访问控制列表（ACL），禁止外部来源向 UDP 端口 9（Discard 端口）发送数据包；如无需 Java Configurator 功能，建议在系统配置中禁用 Discard 服务。鉴于 Ascend MAX/Pipeline/TNT 系列已停止技术支持且无官方补丁可用，建议迁移至受支持的现代路由器硬件以彻底消除风险。作为临时缓解措施，可在网络边界防火墙处过滤目标端口为 UDP 9 的入站流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ascend.com/2695.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19555","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0060","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0060.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/281.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0060.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4/GHSA-5j44-w6q9-hxx4.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/ascend_kill.nasl","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0152.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0768","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0768.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0514","title":"通用网络设备 UDP 广播转发 Fraggle 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"目标系统允许接收发送到广播地址的 UDP 报文，远程攻击者可利用此特性发起 Fraggle 拒绝服务攻击：通过向中间网络的广播地址发送源地址伪造为目标的 UDP 数据包，导致大量响应流量反射至目标系统，造成网络带宽耗尽和服务不可用。此漏洞属于 UDP 反射放大攻击的早期变种，影响广泛支持 UDP 广播的系统和网络设备。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0514"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:33.427","remediation":"在网络边界路由器上执行 `no ip directed-broadcast` 命令禁用定向广播转发；在各接口上实施入口过滤 (ingress filtering, BCP 38)，丢弃源地址非内部网络的入站 UDP 包。同时限制 UDP 广播仅在必要网段开放，并对暴露在公网的 DNS/SNMP/CHARGEN 等 UDP 服务配置速率限制 (rate-limit) 或直接关闭。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0514"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0768.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0752","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0502","title":"Unix SSH 默认空密码远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Unix/Linux 系统存在默认账户密码为空、未设置或使用弱口令的安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过 SSH 服务识别此类弱口令账户，利用 Metasploit 框架等自动化工具进行登录尝试，成功后可获取目标系统的未授权 shell 访问权限，进而执行任意命令或实施横向移动。该漏洞广泛影响各类 Unix/Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。加固措施包括删除或禁用默认账户、强制设置强密码策略。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0502"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.960","remediation":"立即为所有 Unix 系统账户设置强密码（至少 8 位，含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符），禁用空口令账户（`passwd -l` 锁定无密码账户），并配置 `/etc/shadow` 确保口令哈希非空。在 SSH 配置文件 `/etc/ssh/sshd_config` 中设置 `PermitEmptyPasswords no` 并重启 sshd 服务。建议安装并运行 `john` 或 `hydra` 扫描弱口令账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0502","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/41694"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0752.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0545","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0330","title":"Linux bdash 游戏缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Linux bdash 游戏程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向游戏程序提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获取 root 权限，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响运行 bdash 游戏的 Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击前提是攻击者拥有系统的本地账户访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0330"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:10.070","remediation":"立即移除 bdash 游戏的 setuid root 权限位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/games/bdash），或直接卸载 bsdgames 软件包以彻底消除提权风险。如确需保留该游戏，应升级至已修复缓冲区边界检查的修补版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319119&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0545.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0532","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0320","title":"Sun SunOS rpc.cmsd 任意文件覆盖提权漏洞","description":"SunOS/Solaris 系统的 rpc.cmsd（日历管理服务守护进程）存在任意文件覆写漏洞。rpc.cmsd 以 root 权限运行，由于对用户提交的 RPC 参数缺乏充分的路径验证，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的日历管理服务发送特制 RPC 请求，覆写任意系统文件，从而获取 root 访问权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 5.3 至 5.5.1（Solaris 2.3 至 2.5.1）版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0320"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:08.750","remediation":"针对 SunOS/Solaris 2.x 系统，安装 Sun Security Bulletin #166 提供的对应版本补丁：Solaris 2.3 安装 101318 补丁、Solaris 2.4 安装 101945 补丁、Solaris 2.5 安装 103093 补丁、Solaris 2.5.1 安装 103094 补丁。如业务不需要日历管理服务，可停止 rpc.cmsd 守护进程（/etc/init.d/calendar stop）并注释 rpc 绑定条目作为临时缓解。对于仍在运行的遗留系统，建议迁移至 Oracle Solaris 11 及以上受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/166"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0532.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0451","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0266","title":"Info2www CGI 输入处理远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Info2www 是一个用于将 GNU Info 文档转换为 HTML 格式的 CGI 脚本程序。该脚本对用户输入的参数缺乏充分的过滤与验证，远程攻击者可通过向 info2www CGI 脚本发送特制请求，利用输入处理缺陷实现任意文件读取或远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 Info2www 1.0 及 1.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0266"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.100","remediation":"立即从 Web 服务器移除 info2www CGI 脚本目录（通常位于 /cgi-bin/info2www），或删除 info2www 文件。如仍需此类功能，改用维护中的替代方案（如 Pinfo）。通过 Web 服务器配置限制 CGI 目录执行权限，确保仅授权用户可执行，并在 WAF 层过滤包含特殊字符（如 |、;、`、$()）的 CGI 请求参数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1995","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20430","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0266","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0266.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0266.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0266.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr/GHSA-5j6c-65fm-f6cr.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-cgi.rules"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0451.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0484","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0290","title":"Qbik WinGate Telnet Proxy 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qbik WinGate Telnet 代理服务存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者通过向目标系统的 Telnet 代理端口发起大量本地主机连接请求，可耗尽代理服务资源导致服务崩溃，无法正常处理后续合法连接。该漏洞影响 Qbik WinGate 的 Telnet 代理模块，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程触发，风险等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0290"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:04.970","remediation":"建议升级 WinGate 至 4.0 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续迭代中修复。如无法升级，可在 WinGate 网关属性中禁用 telnet 代理服务（取消 Telnet Proxy 复选框），或在防火墙上限制对 telnet 代理端口（默认 23）的入站连接数量，仅允许可信 IP 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0290","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0290.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc/GHSA-m634-4fwc-9xqc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/wingate_denial.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0290.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0484.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0537","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0537.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0323","title":"FreeBSD mmap 函数访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统内核中的 mmap 内存映射函数存在文件属性绕过漏洞，本地攻击者可通过调用 mmap 系统接口，绕过文件系统的保护机制，修改被设置为仅追加（append-only）或不可变（immutable）属性的文件内容。攻击者需要具备目标系统的本地账户权限，通过编写恶意程序调用 mmap 对受保护文件进行写入操作，可导致篡改系统关键配置文件、日志文件或安全策略，破坏系统完整性。该漏洞影响多个 FreeBSD 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0323"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-20T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.107","remediation":"建议升级至 NetBSD 1.4+ 或 FreeBSD 3.0+ 版本，其中已修复 mmap(2) 系统调用对不可变/仅追加文件的权限检查缺陷。对于 NetBSD 1.3/1.3.1，可应用的补丁（来自 ftp://ftp.NetBSD.ORG/pub/NetBSD/misc/security/patches/19980509-mmap）。如无法升级临时缓解措施，可将系统 securelevel 提升至 1 以上并避免在多进程间对设定了 append-only/immutable 标志的文件使用共享可写 mmap。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0323","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0323.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0323.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/057c97aa60eb958a2d272c7164e35c156db63b6c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq/GHSA-r5jc-68gw-7fmq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82264/info.html","https://github.