fc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/b253eed42806cfea7592c1858184a214ab406ebe/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0225.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0225.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000260.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/d6641cf4b3c3f049679d3cd7a1e7c74ad9ced77c/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0411.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0443","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0258","title":"Microsoft Windows 95/NT 4.0 IP Fragmentation 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95 和 Windows NT 4.0 的 IP 碎片重组模块存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送特制的畸形 IP 分片数据包（Bonk 变种），利用 UDP 协议的分片偏移量计算错误，导致目标系统内核崩溃或蓝屏死机，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Windows 95 及 Windows NT 4.0 所有版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0258"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.117","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本系统，已不受此漏洞影响。若因特殊原因仍运行 Windows 95/NT 4.0，安装 Microsoft 1999 年安全更新 MS99-017（KB191725）可修复 IP 分段重组校验逻辑。临时缓解措施：在路由器/防火墙上阻断进入内网的畸形 IP 分片包，或限制入站 ICMP 流量降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=88901842000424&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0258","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0258.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/B/bonk.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0258.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154000_154100.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/e7bd3e92452a8dc8da42d94ae3ba208936d5a5b9/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0443.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0047","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0012","title":"Microsoft Internet Information Server 等多款 Web 服务器文件访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"微软 Windows 平台上的 IIS、FrontPage 及 Personal Web Server 等 Web 服务器存在访问控制绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送包含超长文件名的特制请求，绕过服务器的文件访问限制机制，读取本应受限的系统文件或敏感数据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0、Windows 2000 等系统版本中运行的 IIS 3.0/4.0、Microsoft FrontPage 97/98 及 Personal Web Server 等产品，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.0，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0012"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:20.700","remediation":"建议立即升级至 Windows 2000 及以上操作系统并部署 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，彻底消除此漏洞。若无法升级，可安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-009 提供的修补程序；另在 IIS 管理器中禁用 8.3 短文件名生成，并使用 URLScan 工具过滤包含连续点号、超长文件名段的请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0733","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0486","title":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 超链接远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"AOL Instant Messenger 3.5 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可向目标用户发送特制的恶意超链接，当接收方客户端解析或渲染该链接时触发异常，导致应用程序崩溃。该漏洞利用方式简单，攻击者无需认证即可实施，影响使用 AIM 3.5 版本的用户系统稳定性，属于中等危害级别的拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0486"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.007","remediation":"建议立即升级至 AOL Instant Messenger 4.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复超链接处理逻辑缺陷。由于 AOL 已于 2017 年 12 月 15 日停止 AIM 所有服务且软件不再受支持，当前应从所有设备卸载 AIM，迁移至仍受支持的即时通讯工具，并在防火墙及邮件网关中拦截相关协议的连接请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0486"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0733.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0510","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0305","title":"OpenBSD FreeBSD sysctl 源路由 TCP 连接欺骗漏洞","description":"BSD 系统（包括 OpenBSD 2.2 及更早版本、FreeBSD 2.2.5 及更早版本）的 sysctl 设施在设置 dosourceroute 或 forwarding 变量后，未能正确限制源路由数据包的处理，远程攻击者可利用此缺陷伪造 TCP 连接，绕过访问控制机制实施中间人攻击或会话劫持。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 和 FreeBSD 的早期版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0305"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.863","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 至 2.2.5 以上版本、OpenBSD 至 2.2 以上版本，或在系统配置中设置 sysctl 变量 net.inet.ip.doSourceroute=0 并禁用 IP 转发（sysctl net.inet.ip.forwarding=0），同时在边界防火墙上过滤源路由选项的数据包作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.openbsd.org/advisories/sourceroute.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/11502","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/736"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0510.toml"}]